Transcript: Good evening. You, as a member of the Etobico Lakeshire Liberal Association, are requested to attend a nomination meeting tomorrow, Wednesday, November 30th at 5:30 p.m. at the Valhalla Inn in Etobico at number 1 Valhalla Inn Road, one block south of Brunahorpe turned west off the East Mall. Your attendance is important to support our candidates Marian Schwetz and Roman. If you have any questions, please call at 9. Berman.
